"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-news-world-1878174-french-city-olympics-300000-condoms\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  One village, thousands of super fit people and a lot of spare time.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 69, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This summer, thousands of athletes from around the world will stay in an Olympic Village for the duration of the 2024 ParisOlympicsandParalympics.\", \"from\": 70, \"to\": 216, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 143, \"end\": 158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.998360586287314e-15, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In preparation for the arrival of the world's finest athletes, the director of both events Laurent Michaud said 300,000 condoms would be available to athletes living in the village - enough for each athlete to have sex 21 times.\", \"from\": 218, \"to\": 446, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking toSky Newshe said: \\\"It's a quantity that makes sure that everybody will have what they are expecting and what they need.\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 577, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are going to have 14,250 residents, athletes and press officials over here, that are coming for this great event and to live an extraordinary experience here.\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 739, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We wanted to create some places where the athletes will feel very enthusiastic and comfortable so they can have some conversations, discussions and to share their core values about sports.\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 930, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, we have made a village club with a lounge, with a sports bar with Coca-Cola, and no alcohol of course, but it's going to be a great place so they can share their moment and environment here.\\\"\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 1128, \"entitie