lmost 500,000 tickets sold.\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1515, \"end\": 1525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999986748662, \"rank\": 1.3251357500493708e-09, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1572, \"end\": 1579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9994796964326542, \"rank\": 0.00035942556878482265, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1618, \"end\": 1624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8694696381598488, \"rank\": 0.09617420960021252, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1770, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1847, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 1880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"We are very happy thatTeam GBis coming in force.\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And they will have great expectations.\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The British supporters are very close, it's less than three hours away.London 2012is still in the memories of everyone.\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1998, \"end\": 2005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_King